00055 void test()
00056 {
00057     SHA1Calculator sha1;
00058     sha1.close();
00059     string temp = sha1.hash();
00060     if (os_) *os_ << "hash empty: " << temp << endl;
00061     unit_assert(temp == hashEmpty_);
00062 
00063     sha1.reset();
00064     sha1.update((const unsigned char*)textBrown_, strlen(textBrown_));
00065     sha1.close();
00066     temp = sha1.hash();
00067     if (os_) *os_ << "hash brown: " << temp << endl;
00068     unit_assert(temp == hashBrown_);
00069 }

00117 void testProjected()

00120
